{"tid":1174561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】潘曉穎母校師生發聯署反對 批當局借「公義之名」強行修例","createTime":"2019-05-28T02:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T05:25:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1077dec2a10a1cb8c39b68ceeebec712ff72060f","tid":1174561,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T02:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EdRpx6WjHTbPkFkRo89kQQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190528a071647.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FEdRpx6WjHTbPkFkRo89kQQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190528a071647.jpg&h=84d04140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》修例引起極大爭議，事件源於台灣殺人案，女死者潘曉穎生前就讀的中學赤柱聖士提反書院校友、學生及教師，昨日發聯署聲明，批評當局「假借公義之名」強行修例，到時或引至案件無從處理，「政府之顏面何存？為死者申寃之機何在？」<br />\n<br />\n聯署聲明由兩名老師鍾關錦嫦、陳國培，以及舊生方鎮江和曾子龍發起。聲明指，師生校友對潘曉穎寃死無不痛心疾首，但眼見政府對台灣當局之提案未作積極回應，「卻假借公義之名，強行修例，到時或引至案件無從處理，政府之顏面何存？為死者申寃之機何在？」<br />\n<br />\n聲明續指，香港及國際社會對中國現存司法及其執行部門未具信心，要求特區政府在社會異議不斷的情況下，先行收回條例，擴大社會諮詢，尋求社會大眾最大共識，呼籲政府勿一意孤行，斷送香港前途。聲明提到，應尋求「港人港審」、「 日落條款」等其他可行之法，或設專人與台灣當局進行實際有效的商議，處理今次案件，表明「勿以此案作修例的借口，徒令生者哀傷，死者含恨」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%BD%98%E6%9B%89%E7%A9%8E%E6%AF%8D%E6%A0%A1%E5%B8%AB%E7%94%9F%E7%99%BC%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-%E6%89%B9%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E5%80%9F-%E5%85%AC%E7%BE%A9%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8D-%E5%BC%B7%E8%A1%8C%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-231000005.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%25BD%2598%25E6%259B%2589%25E7%25A9%258E%25E6%25AF%258D%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D-%25E6%2589%25B9%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%2580%259F-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%2590%258D-%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B-231000005.html&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=39c69bbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%BD%98%E6%9B%89%E7%A9%8E%E6%AF%8D%E6%A0%A1%E5%B8%AB%E7%94%9F%E7%99%BC%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-%E6%89%B9%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E5%80%9F-%E5%85%AC%E7%BE%A9%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8D-%E5%BC%B7%E8%A1%8C%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-231000005.html</a>"},{"pid":"0d61570913906d7d79ef5c6694017e8786926b31","tid":1174561,"uid":60648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T04:48:33.000Z","msg":"個女仔既老豆老母走去搵保皇狗對唔對得住自己個v <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖則條女派帽唔抵幫"},{"pid":"8eb521fc983c2c8d6ab39cf01cfc857a5a6d5ef0","tid":1174561,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}